        <Parent_String>pressure welding [300053975], welding [300053958], metal assembling processes and techniques [300053948], metalworking processes and techniques [300053947], metalworking and metalworking processes and techniques [300155055], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
